.SH NAME
hvc_iucv_msg_pending \- IUCV handler to process an incoming IUCV message.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" hvc_iucv_msg_pending
.BI "(struct iucv_path *path "  ","
.BI "struct iucv_message *msg "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "path" 12
Pending path (struct iucv_path)
.IP "msg" 12
Pointer to the IUCV message
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
The function puts an incoming message on the input queue for later
processing (by \fBhvc_iucv_get_chars\fP / \fBhvc_iucv_write\fP).
If the tty has not yet been opened, the message is rejected.

Locking:     struct hvc_iucv_private->lock
